        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 62 of a 12-week money program. The script targets the internal conflict around what wealth 'should' look like: the worry that affluence means leaving behind the simple pleasures, or that enjoying simple pleasures means you're not serious about wealth. The reframe holds both.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
